{"tid":1506201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"企業鑽漏洞躲川普關稅 美國海關盯上","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T01:36:34.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2e85e5ea4963a1e25db1b40b87990a944097e7d1","tid":1506201,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:39:06.000Z","msg":"企業鑽漏洞躲川普關稅 美國海關盯上<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6467657/article-%e4%bc%81%e6%a5%ad%e9%91%bd%e6%bc%8f%e6%b4%9e%e8%ba%b2%e5%b7%9d%e6%99%ae%e9%97%9c%e7%a8%85-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e6%b5%b7%e9%97%9c%e7%9b%af%e4%b8%8a/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6467657%2Farticle-%25e4%25bc%2581%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e9%2591%25bd%25e6%25bc%258f%25e6%25b4%259e%25e8%25ba%25b2%25e5%25b7%259d%25e6%2599%25ae%25e9%2597%259c%25e7%25a8%2585-%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e9%2597%259c%25e7%259b%25af%25e4%25b8%258a%2F&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=650d095b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6467657/article-%e4%bc%81%e6%a5%ad%e9%91%bd%e6%bc%8f%e6%b4%9e%e8%ba%b2%e5%b7%9d%e6%99%ae%e9%97%9c%e7%a8%85-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e6%b5%b7%e9%97%9c%e7%9b%af%e4%b8%8a/</a><br />\n<br />\n總統川普對中國貨物加徵關稅，讓廠商頭痛。不過，部分中國生產商和美國進口商利用法規漏洞，躲避關稅的衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n美國1930年關稅法321條（Section 321 of the Tariff Act of 1930）允許個人或企業在24小時內免稅進口不超過800美元的單件貨物。<br />\n<br />\n南華早報報導，美國前總統歐巴馬在2016年為了促進電商發展，將321條款中的免稅門檻從200美元調高至800美元。現任總統川普開始對中國商品加徵關稅後，該條款變得格外重要。<br />\n<br />\n許多廠商運用該條款，化整為零避稅，已經引起美國海關注意。<br />\n<br />\n美國海關22日展開一年的試辦措施，請運用321條款的業者自願提前申報相關資料。外界專家表示，這是美國海關打擊漏洞的第一步。<br />\n<br />\n深圳一家貨運公司老闆表示，他低報運往美國的貨物價格，以符合321條款。「我知道這項條款...申報真實價值不切實際。不過，這當然有風險，一旦美國海關發現，就會沒收貨物」。<br />\n<br />\n有倉儲物流業者採用「轉運配送」（drop shipping），幫美國客戶免稅進口商品。轉運配送的零售商從未實際接觸到貨物，貨物會直接運送給消費者。<br />\n<br />\n這些產品在中國南部製造後運到香港。消費者在網路下訂單後，商品會出現在香港倉儲設施的管理系統，工作人員撿貨包裝後出貨到美國，由於每件商品的進口人、也就是終端消費者不同，且價值不超過800美元，進入美國時不用繳關稅。接著，商品透過貨運公司送到美國消費者手上。<br />\n<br />\n除了321條款，美企也利用加拿大避稅。他們先將貨物運送到加拿大，接著再用卡車運送至美國，躲避美國針對中國商品加徵的關稅。"},{"pid":"a97feb14ae2a6f50831549d2b237f2df050aa27d","tid":1506201,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:44:31.000Z","msg":"唔係咁天真啊⋯有無睇清楚美國法例啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451be84be2e778995524c631da86f8256538544e","tid":1506201,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0bf044de619f009cd598557018883cfe8f4ab1","tid":1506201,"uid":29899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:19:37.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=cb434dae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9dab0b5137c4301d04b20f180c17a39a8332aa1","tid":1506201,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:23:02.000Z","msg":"這些產品在中國南部製造後運到香港。消費者在網路下訂單後，商品會出現在香港倉儲設施的管理系統，工作人員撿貨包裝後出貨到美國<br />\n<br />\n用埋香港逃稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3cf1057d5293e0777d61047851309d6461939c","tid":1506201,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"你當你d人民傻<br />\n你唔係當埋美國傻吓話?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778e16edbf603b779b5ca082a834af1ea23dda55","tid":1506201,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:36:34.000Z","msg":"又係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}